properties.name: Path
properties.expression: function lowerStrokePath() {        const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');        const curveLin = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('curvature').value[1] * 0.01;        if (curveLin === 0) {            return createPath([                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value,                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p2ikfkfreek').value,            ], [], [], false);        }        else {            const inTangPos = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('inTangPos').value;            const outTangPos = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('outTangPos').value;            return createPath([                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value,                endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p2ikfkfreek').value,            ], [inTangPos, [0, 0]], [mul(outTangPos, -1), [0, 0]], false);        }    }lowerStrokePath();

properties.expression: let val = [100, 100]if (thisLayer.hasParent) {    const ctrlScaleFactor = Math.max(thisLayer.length(thisLayer.toComp([0, 0]), thisLayer.toComp([0.7071, 0.7071])), 0.0001);    val = [value[0] / ctrlScaleFactor, value[1] / ctrlScaleFactor]}val
